# 更改dataset钟的列名，将其输出成backtrader适配的形式
def get_data(code,start,end,word):
    df = pd.read_csv(code+".csv")
    show = ['ts']
    for i in df.columns:
        if word in i:
            show.append(i)
    df = df[show]
    df['openinterest']=0
    df.columns = ['date','open','high','low','close','volume','openinterest']
    df['volume'] = 10000
    df.index=pd.to_datetime(df.date)
    df = df.drop(["date"],axis = 1)
    #df.date = df.date.apply(lambda x: x.split(" ")[0])
    
    
    df = df.sort_index()
    df = df.fillna(method="ffill",axis=0)
    df = df.fillna(method="bfill",axis=0)
    return df

# 策略编写部分
import datetime  # For datetime objects
import backtrader as bt

# Create a Stratey
class TestStrategy(bt.Strategy):
    params = (('BBandsperiod', 20),('devfactor', 2),
              ('max_hold', 10),('d',20),
              ('e',10),('each_order',1))

    def log(self, txt, dt=None):
        ''' Logging function fot this strategy'''
        dt =  self.datas[0].datetime.date(0)
        print(str(dt), txt, ',position size',self.position.size)

    def __init__(self):
        # Keep a reference to the "close" line in the data[0] dataseries
        self.dataclose = self.datas[0].close
        # To keep track of pending orders and buy price/commission
        self.order = None
        self.buyprice = None
        self.buycomm = None
        self.sellcomm = None
        self.redline = None
        self.blueline = None
        self.sellprice = None
        self.val_start = self.broker.get_cash()
        # Add a BBand indicator
        self.bband = bt.indicators.BBands(self.datas[0], 
                                          period=self.params.BBandsperiod,
                                          devfactor=self.params.devfactor,
                                          plotskip = True)
        self.open_price = 0
        self.last_closing_price = 0
        self.trade_close = self.datas[0].close
        self.trade_open = self.datas[0].open
        self.trade_high = self.datas[0].high
        self.trade_low = self.datas[0].low
        
        self.bid_high = self.datas[1].high
        self.bid_low = self.datas[1].low
        self.bid_open = self.datas[1].open
        self.bid_close = self.datas[1].close
        
        self.ask_high = self.datas[2].high
        self.ask_low = self.datas[2].low
        self.ask_open = self.datas[2].open
        self.ask_close = self.datas[2].close
        
        self.trade_band = bt.indicators.BollingerBands(self.trade_close,
                period=self.params.BBandsperiod,devfactor=self.params.devfactor)
        self.bid_band = bt.indicators.BollingerBands(self.bid_close,
                period=self.params.BBandsperiod,devfactor=self.params.devfactor,plotskip = True)
        self.ask_band = bt.indicators.BollingerBands(self.ask_close,
                period=self.params.BBandsperiod,devfactor=self.params.devfactor,plotskip = True)
        
    def notify_order(self, order):
        if order.status in [order.Submitted, order.Accepted]:
            # Buy/Sell order submitted/accepted to/by broker - Nothing to do
            return
        # Check if an order has been completed
        # Attention: broker could reject order if not enougth cash
        if order.status in [order.Completed]:
            if order.isbuy():
                self.log(
                    'LONG EXECUTED, Price: %.2f, Cost: %.2f, Comm %.2f' %
                    (order.executed.price,
                     order.executed.value,
                     order.executed.comm))
                # 记录开仓价格
                if self.open_create_target == 1:
                    self.open_price = order.executed.price
                # 记录平仓价格
                if self.closing_target == 1:
                    self.last_closing_price = order.executed.price
                #self.last_closing_price = order.executed.price
                self.buyprice = order.executed.price
                self.buycomm = order.executed.comm
            else:  # Sell
                self.log(
                    'SHORT EXECUTED, Price: %.2f, Cost: %.2f, Comm %.2f' %
                    (order.executed.price,
                     -order.executed.value,
                     order.executed.comm))
                # 记录开仓价格
                if self.open_create_target == 1:
                    self.open_price = order.executed.price
                # 记录平仓价格
                if self.closing_target == 1:
                    self.last_closing_price = order.executed.price
                #self.last_closing_price = order.executed.price
                self.sellprice = order.executed.price
                self.sellcomm = order.executed.comm
            self.bar_executed = len(self)
        elif order.status in [order.Canceled, order.Margin, 
                              order.Rejected]:
            self.log('Order Canceled/Margin/Rejected')
        # Write down: no pending order
        self.order = None
    def notify_trade(self, trade):
        if not trade.isclosed:
            return

        self.log('OPERATION PROFIT, GROSS %.2f, NET %.2f' %
                 (trade.pnl, trade.pnlcomm))
        
    def notify_cashvalue(self, cash, value):
        self.vals = value
        print('PnL' + str(self.vals - self.val_start))
        
    def next(self):
        self.executed_target = 0
        self.closing_target = 0
        self.create_target = 0
        self.open_create_target = 0
        # Simply log the closing price of the series from the reference
        self.log('Close, %.2f' % self.trade_close[0])
        if len(self.trade_close) == 626:
            self.close(exectype = bt.Order.Market)
        # Check if an order is pending ... if yes, we cannot send a 2nd one
        if self.order:
            return
        
        # 买仓开仓逻辑 
        if self.ask_close > self.ask_band.lines.top:
            if (self.ask_close - self.last_closing_price) > self.params.e:
                if self.position.size >= 0:
                    self.order = self.buy(size = min(self.params.each_order, self.params.max_hold - self.position.size),
                                           exectype = bt.Order.Market)
                    self.open_create_target = 1
                    self.log('LONG CREATE, %.2f' % self.ask_close[0])
                    return 
        # 卖仓开仓逻辑
        if self.bid_close < self.bid_band.lines.bot:
            if (self.bid_close - self.last_closing_price) > self.params.e:
                if self.position.size <= 0:
                    self.order = self.sell(size = min(self.params.each_order, self.params.max_hold + self.position.size), 
                                           exectype = bt.Order.Market)
                    self.open_create_target = 1
                    self.log('SHORT CREATE, %.2f' % self.bid_close[0])
                    return
        
        
        if self.position.size > 0:
            # 多头止盈逻辑
            if self.trade_open - self.open_price > self.params.d:
                self.close(exectype = bt.Order.Market)
                self.closing_target = 1
                return
            # 多头止损逻辑
            elif self.open_price - self.trade_open > self.params.d:
                self.close(exectype = bt.Order.Market)
                self.closing_target = 1
                return
        
        if self.position.size < 0:
            # 空头止盈逻辑
            if self.open_price - self.trade_open > self.params.d:
                self.close(exectype = bt.Order.Market)
                self.closing_target = 1
                return
            # 空头止损逻辑
            elif self.trade_open - self.open_price > self.params.d:
                self.close(exectype = bt.Order.Market)
                self.closing_target = 1
                return

# Set our desired cash start

# Add a FixedSize sizer according to the stake

# Print out the starting conditions

# Run over everything
cerebro.run()

# Print out the final result
print('Final Portfolio Value: %.2f' % cerebro.broker.getvalue())
